main.java.sorter

Class ResultGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.sorter.ResultGenerator

  • public class ResultGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Generates results based on configuration file. Will generate results with all data, including possible error messages and a sorted result file in placement order. These two versions are also saved in HTML format.
    Author:
    team03
